3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fetf-investing-noj-us-stocks-developed-emerging-markets-sell-america-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EStocks%20outside%20the%20US%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20been%20big%20winners%20this%20year%20as%20factors%20like%20tariffs%2C%20rate%20cuts%2C%20growing%20government%20debt%2C%20and%20a%20decline%20in%20investor%20confidence%20have%20weakened%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Findex%2Fus-dollar-index%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EUS%20dollar%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBlackRock%20says%20the%20trend%20is%20likely%20just%20getting%20started.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20believe%20we%20are%20toward%20the%20beginning%20of%20a%20weaker%20dollar%20cycle%2C%20which%20has%20tended%20to%20boost%20international%20returns%20%E2%80%94%20potentially%20indicating%20a%20structural%20relationship%20change%20that%20requires%20investors%20to%20consider%20evolving%20portfolio%20construction%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20firm%20said%20in%20an%20August%2029%20report%20authored%20by%20Gargi%20Pal%20Chaudhuri%20and%20Kristy%20Akullian.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20continued%3A%20%26quot%3BThe%20dollar%20has%20long%20benefited%20from%20a%20cycle%20of%20robust%20US%20growth%20and%20investment.%20But%20we%20think%20the%20structural%20bull%20market%20may%20be%20challenged%20amid%20current%20trade%20policy%20and%20demand%20for%20alternative%20reserve%20currencies.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20numbers%20support%20this%20view.%20Dollar%20weakening%20cycles%20since%20the%201970s%20have%20lasted%20an%20average%20of%20eight%20years%2C%20the%20firm%20said.%20The%20current%20cycle%20is%20less%20than%20three%20years%20old.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221602%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22fx%20cycle%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68b8838a32af4d666ef72cc0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221110%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EiShares%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20how%20to%20invest%20around%20the%20trend%2C%20the%20firm%20said%20that%20%26quot%3Bunhedged%20international%20equities%20may%20stand%20to%20benefit%20the%20most%20from%20ongoing%20currency%20weakness.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInvesting%20in%20unhedged%20international%20stocks%20means%20having%20exposure%20to%20them%20in%20their%20local%20currencies.%20That%20way%2C%20if%20that%20currency%20rises%20relative%20to%20the%20dollar%2C%20your%20total%20return%20in%20dollars%20is%20larger.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20if%20the%20foreign%20currency%20falls%20relative%20to%20the%20dollar%2C%20it%20eats%20into%20your%20total%20returns.%20Investors%20can%20choose%20to%20hedge%20their%20investments%20in%20foreign%20stocks%2C%20which%20takes%20the%20currency%20volatility%20out%20of%20the%20equation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBlackRock%20has%20multiple%20unhedged%20international%20stock%20ETFs%2C%20like%20the%20iShares%20Core%20MSCI%20Total%20International%20Stock%20ETF%20(IXUS).%20Other%20examples%20include%20the%20Vanguard%20Total%20International%20Stock%20ETF%20(VXUS)%20and%20the%20Schwab%20Emerging%20Markets%20Equity%20ETF%20(SCHE).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EData%20shows%20investors%20are%20still%20overconcentrated%20in%20US%20stocks%2C%20BlackRock%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20average%20advisor%20allocates%2077.5%25%20of%20their%20equity%20portfolio%20to%20the%20US%2C%20up%20from%2070%25%20in%202018%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20firm%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20money%20is%20starting%20to%20move%20overseas%2C%20with%20the%20portion%20of%20ETF%20inflows%20going%20to%20international%20funds%20up%20to%2029%25%20from%2012%25%20in%20August%20last%20year.%20That%20has%20coincided%20with%20strong%20performance%20in%20overseas%20stocks.%20IXUS%20is%20up%2020%25%20in%202025%20compared%20to%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500's%209%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-outlook-us-vs-international-stocks-recession-trade-war-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EBank%20of%20America%20survey%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20fund%20managers%20earlier%20this%20year%20showed%20that%2054%25%20of%20the%20group%20thinks%20international%20stocks%20will%20be%20the%20best-performing%20trade%20over%20the%20next%20five%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20case%20of%20a%20recession%2C%20BlackRock%20said%20that%20international%20stocks%20may%20be%20a%20better%20portfolio%20diversifier%20than%20US%20small-caps%2C%20which%20are%20subject%20to%20the%20same%20macro%20forces%20that%20large-cap%20US%20firms%20are.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLower%20correlation%20and%20corporate%20reforms%20in%20certain%20parts%20of%20the%20world%20suggest%20that%20most%20investors%20could%20benefit%20unconditionally%20from%20owning%20more%20international%20stocks%20and%20seeking%20alpha%20in%20international%20markets%20as%20well%20as%20the%20U.S.%20markets%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Phil%20Hodges%2C%20co-lead%20of%20the%20Systematic%20Equities%20Macro%20Group%20at%20BlackRock%2C%20in%20a%20quote%20included%20in%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-invest-to-benefit-from-weaker-us-dollar-blackrock-2025-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1756994301000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68b8842e57d362d375e772a6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-invest-to-benefit-from-weaker-us-dollar-blackrock-2025-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Dollar%20weakening%20cycles%20since%20the%201970s%20have%20lasted%20an%20average%20of%20eight%20years%2C%20BlackRock%20says.%20The%20current%20cycle%20is%20less%20than%20three%20years%20old.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22wedwards%40businessinsider.com%20(William%20Edwards)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-invest-to-benefit-from-weaker-us-dollar-blackrock-2025-