pressed%20me%20most%20is%20that%20the%20inverter%20draws%20daytime%20electricity%20directly%20from%20solar.%20Once%20the%20battery%20is%20charged%2C%20iCUBE%20shuts%20off%20the%20KSEB%20supply.%20If%20the%20sunlight%20is%20good%2C%20you%20can%20run%20600%E2%80%93700%20watts%20straight%20from%20solar.%20If%20the%20consumption%20exceeds%20that%2C%20it%20switches%20to%20KSEB%20seamlessly.%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20even%20notice%20the%20transition%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Suresh%2C%20who%20lives%20in%20the%20Aliparamba%20village.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fsolar-inverter-1-1756908818.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20iCON%20device%20enables%20households%20to%20connect%20their%20old%20inverters%20to%20solar%20panels%2C%20fostering%20affordable%20transition%20to%20solar%20energy.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fsolar-inverter-1-1756908818.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fsolar-inverter-1-1756908818-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fsolar-inverter-1-1756908818-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fsolar-inverter-1-1756908818-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fsolar-inverter-1-1756908818-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-495988%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20iCON%20device%20enables%20households%20to%20connect%20their%20old%20inverters%20to%20solar%20panels%2C%20fostering%20an%20affordable%20transition%20to%20solar%20energy.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20year%E2%80%99s%20monsoon%20put%20the%20system%20to%20the%20test.%20A%20storm%20destroyed%2025%20electricity%20poles%20and%20blacked%20out%20his%20neighbourhood%20for%20five%20days.%20Yet%20Suresh%E2%80%99s%20house%20and%20office%20remained%20powered.%20%E2%80%9CFor%20that%20entire%20week%2C%20I%20was%20practically%20off-grid.%20My%20work%20didn%E2%80%99t%20stop%20even%20when%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20street%20was%20dark.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20student%20idea%20that%20became%20a%20solar%20revolution%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuresh%E2%80%99s%20story%20reflects%20exactly%20what%20Harsh%20Mohan%20(34)%2C%20co-founder%20of%20Energy24by7%2C%20and%20his%20peers%20dreamt%20of%20back%20in%202011.%20Then%20undergraduates%20at%20Amrita%20Vishwa%20Vidyapeetham%2C%20Amritapuri%2C%20they%20were%20searching%20for%20a%20meaningful%20project%20when%20they%20stumbled%20upon%20something%20simple%20but%20striking%3A%20nearly%20every%20household%20in%20India%20had%20an%20inverter%2C%20but%20these%20machines%20consumed%20power%20daily%20just%20to%20stay%20alive%2C%20often%20adding%201.5%20to%20two%20units%20to%20the%20bill%20per%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20solar%20was%20making%20headlines%2C%20but%20at%20a%20steep%20cost%2C%E2%80%9D%20Harsh%20recalls.%20%E2%80%9CInstalling%20rooftop%20solar%20meant%20discarding%20your%20existing%20inverter%20and%20buying%20a%20new%2C%20solar-compatible%20one.%20It%20was%20unaffordable%20for%20most%20families%20and%20created%20huge%20amounts%20of%20e-waste.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20challenge%20sparked%20an%20idea.%20Guided%20by%20his%20professor%20Dr%20Vinod%20Gopal%2C%20Harsh%20began%20tinkering%20with%20a%20solution%3A%20What%20if%2C%20instead%20of%20replacing%20inverters%2C%20they%20could%20create%20a%20small%20device%20that%20connected%20any%20inverter%20to%20solar%20panels%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReiterating%20this%20idea%2C%20Nishanth%20CP%2C%20co-founder%20of%20Energy24by7%2C%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CThat%20way%2C%20households%20could%20adopt%20solar%20without%20buying%20a%20new%20system%2C%20reducing%20both%20costs%20and%20pollution.%20Our%20aim%20was%20to%20make%20solar%20accessible%20to%20middle-class%20families%2C%20not%20just%20the%20wealthy.%20Back%20then%2C%20panels%20were%20very%20expensive%2C%20and%20people%20thought%20solar%20was%20only%20for%20the%20rich.%20We%20wanted%20to%20change%20that.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20device%20became%20%E2%80%98iCON%E2%80%99%20(Intelligent%20Converter).%20%E2%80%9CSuddenly%2C%20families%20didn%E2%80%99t%20need%20to%20spend%20lakhs%20on%20a%20new%20solar%20system.%20With%20a%20modest%20investment%20in%20iCON%20and%20panels%2C%20they%20could%20turn%20their%20old%20inverters%20into%20solar%20inverters%20overnight%2C%E2%80%9D%20Harsh%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fsolar-inverter-4-1756908948.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22From%20Left%3A%20Harsh%20Mohan%2C%20Dr%20Vinod%20Kumar%20Gopal%2C%20Nishanth%20CP%2C%20Lakshmi%20Nambiar%2C%20Kiran%20S.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fsolar-inverter-4-1756908948.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fsolar-inverter-4-1756908948-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fsolar-inverter-4-1756908948-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fsolar-inverter-4-1756908948-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fsolar-inverter-4-1756908948-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-495993%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EFrom%20Left%3A%20Harsh%20Mohan%2C%20Dr%20Vinod%20Kumar%20Gopal%2C%20Nishanth%20CP%2C%20Lakshmi%20Nambiar%2C%20Kiran%20S.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202017%2C%20after%20nearly%20five%20years%20of%20product%20iterations%20and%20patent%20work%2C%20Harsh%20and%20his%20colleagues%2C%20Dr%20Vinod%20Gopal%2C%20Lakshmi%20Nambiar%2C%20Nishanth%20CP%2C%20and%20Kiran%20S%2C%20formally%20launched%20%E2%80%98NyQuest%20Innovation%20Labs%20Pvt%20Ltd%E2%80%99.%20The%20company%20was%20later%20rebranded%20as%20Energy24by7%20to%20make%20the%20brand%20more%20customer-friendly%20and%20mission-driven.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETurning%20feedback%20into%20a%20smarter%20inverter%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20launch%20of%20iCON%20opened%20doors%2C%20but%20customer%20feedback%20soon%20pushed%20the%20team%20further.%20%E2%80%9CMany%20people%20told%20us%20their%20old%20inverters%20were%20noisy%2C%20inefficient%2C%20and%20bulky%2C%E2%80%9D%20Harsh%20recalls.%20%E2%80%9CSo%20we%20decided%20to%20build%20a%20new%20solar%20inverter%20on%20our%20own.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20result%20was%20%E2%80%98iCUBE%E2%80%99%2C%20a%20high-efficiency%20smart%20solar%20UPS%20that%20brought%20together%20the%20roles%20of%20iCON%20and%20a%20regular%20inverter%20in%20one%20device.%20%E2%80%9CMost%20inverters%20in%20India%20run%20at%20a%20lower%20efficiency%2C%20but%20iCUBE%20tested%20at%20an%20impressive%20peak%20efficiency%20of%2097%20percent%E2%80%94making%20it%20even%20better%20than%20the%20benchmark%20five-star%20standards%2C%E2%80%9D%20Harsh%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeyond%20efficiency%2C%20iCUBE%20was%20designed%20to%20adapt%20to%20household%20usage%20patterns%2C%20deciding%20when%20to%20use%20solar%2C%20when%20to%20draw%20from%20batteries%2C%20and%20when%20to%20tap%20into%20the%20grid.%20Their%20patented%20Battery%20Charging%20Inhibition%20(BCI)%20prevents%20wasteful%20charging%20from%20the%20grid%2C%20cutting%20hidden%20costs%20that%20many%20households