9CThe%20biggest%20challenge%20has%20always%20been%20funding%2C%E2%80%9D%20admits%20co-founder%20Nishanth.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20India%E2%80%99s%20startup%20ecosystem%2C%20hardware%20rarely%20gets%20the%20same%20attention%20as%20software.%20Investors%20like%20fast-scaling%20apps%20with%20quick%20returns.%20But%20hardware%20requires%20long-term%20investment%2C%20multiple%20prototypes%2C%20and%20a%20lot%20of%20testing.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENishanth%20adds%20that%20every%20time%20they%20set%20up%20a%20system%20in%20someone%E2%80%99s%20home%2C%20they%20would%20discover%20something%20new%20the%20customer%20wanted.%20That%20meant%20going%20back%2C%20redesigning%2C%20and%20swapping%20out%20parts%20%E2%80%94%20a%20slow%2C%20painstaking%20process%20that%20most%20investors%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20the%20patience%20for.%20What%20kept%20them%20going%20were%20the%20central%20and%20state%20government%20grants%20and%20support%20programmes%2C%20especially%20from%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Electronics%2C%20which%20gave%20them%20the%20runway%20they%20needed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20Kerala%20to%20the%20world%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20Energy24by7%20has%20more%20than%201%2C000%20customers%20across%20Kerala%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20and%20Karnataka%2C%20and%20is%20also%20making%20inroads%20into%20Africa%20with%20installations%20in%20Kenya%20and%20Zambia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fsolar-inverter-3-1756908919.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Energy24by7%20developed%20the%20iCUBE%2C%20a%20more%20efficient%20and%20integrated%20solar%20UPS%20that%20ensures%20up%20to%2097%25%20energy%20efficiency.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fsolar-inverter-3-1756908919.jpg%201200w